title: Can't place WhatsApp calls when using mobile data. I can't hear the other end and they can't hear me
content: Unable to place whatsapp calls when using mobile data. It shows it's connecting but can't hear the other end and they can't hear me. Any ideas on what's happening? This changed after I did the Android 10 update.
category: Connectivity, Network, Bluetooth, Google Pixel 3a XL
